FBIS4-7827 "dreeu067_i_94010" FBIS-EEU-94-067 Daily Report 6 Apr 1994 BOSNIA-HERZEGOVINA Battle for Gorazde Continuing Battle for Gorazde Continuing UN: `Gorazde No Longer Under Attack' AU0604165794 Paris AFP in English 1637 GMT 6 Apr 94 AU0604165794 Paris AFP English BFN [Text] United Nations, April 6 (AFP) -- Bosnian Serbs besieging the Moslem enclave of Gorazde in Bosnia-Herzegovina stopped their shelling late Wednesday [6 April], a UN spokesman said Wednesday. "Gorazde is no longer under attack since 1800 local time," the spokesman, Joe Sills said. Sills said that the UN representative in Bosnia Yasushi Akashi had received assurance from the Bosnian Serbs that the attacks would not resume.
